Class ArtefactIterator

java.lang.Object
  de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.model.datastructure.ArtefactIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Iterator<MetaClass>
public class ArtefactIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<MetaClass>

It provides an way to access the elements of Artefact data structure sequentially. It is intended to use it as an iterator for all lists at once. If you need the possibility to iterator through all elements, without worrying about specify artefact types you should use this.
